definition: to lay/to place/to put in a certain place
content/calm/still/quiet/safe/secure/in good health/to find a place for/to install/to fix/to fit/to bring (a charge against sb)/to pacify/to harbor (good intentions)/security/safety/peace/ampere
to put/to place/to release/to free/to let go/to let out/to set off (fireworks)

sentences.english: Place the double layered tempered safety glass door on top of the enclosure.
sentences.chinese: 把雙層鋼化安全玻璃門安放在水箱頂。

sentences.english: His ashes lie in the same Roman cemetery where Keats is buried.
sentences.chinese: 他的骨灰安放在羅馬公墓，濟慈也安葬於此。

sentences.english: When the steel was placed in ice water and hit with a hammer, it shattered.
sentences.chinese: 當鋼鐵被安放在冰水中並用錘子敲打時，它碎掉了。

sentences.english: The first eight stupas were created to hold the Buddha's remains.
sentences.chinese: 最初的八座佛塔中安放的就是釋迦牟尼的佛骨舍利。

sentences.english: Install dipstick and verify it is seated in the tube.
sentences.chinese: 安裝引擎機油尺並確認它安放在管中。

sentences.english: French townspeople lay flowers on the body of an American soldier.
sentences.chinese: 法國市民在美軍士兵屍體上安放鮮花。

sentences.english: The ideal place for a desk would be in a den or office.
sentences.chinese: 安放桌子的理想地方應該在小房間或辦公室裏。

sentences.english: It was time for me to work on the hoops and battens.
sentences.chinese: 現在是我在安放箍和壓條。

sentences.english: What a squiffy life?How can I emplace you, my prime?
sentences.chinese: 這微醉的人生呵，如何安放你我的青春？

sentences.english: We have intelligence about all the stationery SAM sites and high-speed missiles.
sentences.chinese: 我們擁有所有那些高速導彈及其安放地點的情報。

sentences.english: The conception on an insertion mechanism of nonrigid flat inserts was firstly suggested by us.
sentences.chinese: 首次提出了片狀非剛性嵌件安放機構的設計構思。

sentences.english: The photodiode is placed in an electrically shielded dark box.
sentences.chinese: 該光電二極管安放在一個電屏蔽的暗箱中。

sentences.english: Pad of the foot can be rotated to adjust the angle for easy placement.
sentences.chinese: 肩墊的腳可以旋轉調整角度，便於安放。

sentences.english: We can put sensors in cars.
sentences.chinese: 我們可以在車內安放感應器。

sentences.english: Wreaths were laid at the martyr's tomb.
Position weatherstrip on flange aligning notches in each corner.
sentences.chinese: 將防水飾條安放在與每個角落刻痕對齊的凸緣上。
